Something like
```{% for content in contents %}
    {% if loop.index &lt;= 1 %}
        // First post
    {% endif %}
{% endfor %}```
And to display the rest, continue the loop later:
```{% for content in contents %}
    {% if loop.index &gt; 1 %}
        // The rest
    {% endif %}
{% endfor %}```
This will keep the amount of posts on the page to the value set in the blog settings.
